msgctxt "sn22.113:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.113:0.2"
msgid "12. Dhammakathikavagga"
msgstr "12. A Dhamma speaker"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 113. Avijjāsutta → avijjā or bhikkhu 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.113:0.3"
msgid "113. Avijjāsutta"
msgstr "113. Ignorance"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.163"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.113:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe …"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.3"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.4"
msgid "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’."

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.5"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, avijjā;"
msgstr "What is ignorance?"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.6"
msgid "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr "And how is an ignorant person defined?”"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.7"
msgid ""
"“Idha, bhikkhu, assutavā puthujjano rūpaṃ nappajānāti, rūpasamudayaṃ "
"nappajānāti, rūpanirodhaṃ nappajānāti, rūpanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ "
"nappajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, it’s when an uneducated ordinary person doesn’t understand form, "
"its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its cessation."

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.8"
msgid "vedanaṃ nappajānāti …"
msgstr "They don’t understand feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.9"
msgid "saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.10"
msgid "saṅkhāre nappajānāti … pe …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.11"
msgid "viññāṇanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"consciousness, its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its "
"cessation."

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.12"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, avijjā;"
msgstr "This is called ignorance."

msgctxt "sn22.113:1.13"
msgid "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti."
msgstr "And this is how an ignorant person is defined.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.113:1.14"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
